cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.CL, cs.CR, cs.DB

This paper deals with knowledge representation and reasoning, which is a core topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). It also involves logic programming (cs.LO) and computational logic (cs.CL) as LPMLN is a combination of Answer Set Programming (ASP) and Markov Logic Networks (MLN). The paper also discusses simplifying logic programs and constructing knowledge bases, which are related to databases (cs.DB). Finally, the paper deals with uncertainty and inconsistency, which can be considered as a topic in cryptography and security (cs.CR).
